## Search for companies

> Example Requests

```shell
curl "<%= config.host %>/company/search" \
  -H "<%= config.auth %>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "query": "Netflix"
  }'
```

```shell
curl "<%= config.host %>/company/search" \
  -H "<%= config.auth %>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "category": "gas"
  }'
```

```shell
curl "<%= config.host %>/company/search" \
  -H "<%= config.auth %>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "geo": {
      "lat": 40.233845,
      "lng": -111.65852
    }
  }'
```

